  "title": "Securing Gen AI Apps with Entra 2/4",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael, Gladys and Mark talk with guest Bailey Bercik&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/baileybercik/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about how to use Microsoft Entra Permissions Management to identify and manage over-permissioned identities in multi-cloud environments to reduce security risks.\n\n                  <br>\n                  We also discuss Azure Security news about Lessons from AI red-teaming, Azure Confidential Ledger, Star Blizzard treat actor, and the CISA Zero Trust Maturity Model.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/1902670?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1902670/\">Entra3</a></iframe>\n\n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/NNNNNN/#transcript'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/security/blog/2025/01/13/3-takeaways-from-red-teaming-100-generative-ai-products/\">3 takeaways from red teaming 100 generative AI products</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azuresqlblog/enhanced-server-audit-for-azure-sql-database-greater-performance-availability-an/4366433\">Enhanced Server Audit for Azure SQL Database: Greater Performance, Availability and Reliability\n     